---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Schindler-JP">
  <Container>
    <!-- 公司简介及理念 -->
    <section class="py-10 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">Schindler-JPについて</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">イノベーションと卓越性への情熱で、未来を切り拓くコンサルティング＆AIソリューション企業。<br/>Professional AI & Consulting Team Empowering Your Vision.</p>
    </section>
    <!-- 团队信息区 -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">リーダー＆専門家チーム</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500">Passionate founders & experienced support staff</p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <!-- Row 1 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-white rounded-lg border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">LZ</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-1">Ligong Zheng</h3>
                <div class="text-sm text-purple-600 font-medium mb-2">社長</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">愛知産業大学卒、経営＆日中協業事例多数。幅広い海外ネットワーク。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">JZ</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-1">John Zhang</h3>
                <div class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium mb-2">共同創設者・ロボティクス専門家</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">名古屋大学博士/10年以上AI・ロボ研究開発。LLM・ロボット知能開発に深い見識。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Row 2 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-white rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-500 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">MZ</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-1">Martin Zhang</h3>
                <div class="text-sm text-green-600 font-medium mb-2">共同創設者</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">名古屋大学院卒。DX/IT課題解決の知見豊富なコンサル。自動車＆金融＆保険業界において10年以上DX経験者。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-white rounded-lg border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">HL</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-1">Hualiang Lee</h3>
                <div class="text-sm text-orange-600 font-medium mb-2">共同創設者・法律顧問</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">北京大学法学修士。中日企業/個人の国際法務・資金アドバイス。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Row 3 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-white rounded-lg border-l-4 border-indigo-500 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">SL</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-1">Steven Lin</h3>
                <div class="text-sm text-indigo-600 font-medium mb-2">技術サポートスペシャリスト</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">カリフォルニア大学リバーサイド校卒。豊富な技術知識でシステム導入・運用をサポート。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-white rounded-lg border-l-4 border-pink-500 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">MW</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-1">Maggie Wu</h3>
                <div class="text-sm text-pink-600 font-medium mb-2">シニアコンサルタント</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">京都大学院卒。DX/IT課題解決の知見豊富なコンサル。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- 团队宣言区块 -->
    <section class="py-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">ビジョンとミッション</h2>
      <blockquote class="italic text-lg text-slate-600">“革新的な技術で社会・企業の未来を変革し、専門知識と情熱で最高の価値を提供します。”</blockquote>
    </section>
  </Container>
</Layout>
